<p>^^ cycle through different famous first lines of novels</p>

<p>Let's collaborate together to create the worlds first library of crowdsourced stories, diaries, lyrics, etc. There are no limits; any type of text content is acceptable. The voting process will highlight the most popular content so other users may add to it. If a story takes a complete different directions, that it completely encouraged! This is a experiment to see what comes out. Link specific content to your friends and share via social media/email/etc. Create your own private branches if you have a specific group  of people you would like to collaborate with. Use it as you see fit!</p>

